<p>I am using the below code for fetching data from live server...</p>  <pre><code>try             {     var httpReq = (HttpWebRequest)HttpWebRequest.Create(new Uri(url_builder.ToString()));                 httpReq.BeginGetResponse((ar) =&gt;                 {                         var request = (HttpWebRequest)ar.AsyncState;                          using (var response = (HttpWebResponse)request.EndGetResponse(ar))                         {                              //Enter Code here............................                              response.Close();                         }                 });                 }, httpReq);  }             catch (Exception ex)             {                 Global.EmailExceptionMessage(ex);             } </code></pre>  <p>And getting inner exception i.e.</p>  <p>Inner Exception:   at System.Net.WebConnection.HandleError(WebExceptionStatus st, System.Exception e, System.String where)    at System.Net.WebConnection.ReadDone(IAsyncResult result)</p>